message.content:
Let's write down the family tree of Sally and her brothers to make it easier to count the number of sisters:


|Sally|Brother1|Brother2|Brother3|
|-----|-------|-------|-------|
|      |       |       |       |
|      |     /  \   |     /  \ |
|      |    SisA1  |   SisB1  |
|      |         |        |     |
|      |         |        |  /  \
|SisC1 |        |    SisC2 |  |
|     |        |        | /    \
|     |        |       |SisD1  |

There are a total of four sisters in the family: SisA1, SisB1, SisC1 and SisD1. Therefore, Sally has three sisters.
